{"type":"message","id":"592b7731","parentId":"72c94934","timestamp":"2026-05-17T01:00:00.166Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 17th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-17 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1778979600164}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3f6642c","parentId":"592b7731","timestamp":"2026-05-17T01:02:20.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job triggering the daily reminder about Cursor collaboration rules. The task says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, just silently confirm). \n\nHowever, the cron system expects a summary to be returned. Let me check - this is a cron event that fires daily at 09:00. The instruction says to return summary as plain text and it will be delivered automatically. But also says \"note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself\" if the task calls for messaging.\n\nThis is just a reminder/notification, not an actual task to execute. The rules are already in AGENTS.md. I should just return a brief confirmation that the rules are remembered.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - this is a cron job that injects a system event. The format says \"Return your summary as plain text\" so I should just output a brief acknowledgment."},{"type":"text","text":"✅ Cursor 协作规则已确认，今日刷新时间：2026-05-17 09:00。规则要点：\n1. 用户要求 Cursor 任务 → submit_task.py --notify\n2. 用户回复确认消息 → confirm_write.py --decision auto\n3. 查看任务队列 → submit_task.py --list\n4. 查看完成结果 → submit_task.py --results"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778979600165}}
